  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261804</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_250_020_000</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;ヴァルハラ&lt;White&gt;の街にも少しずつ
人が戻り始め、元の賑わいを
取り戻していました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The people of &lt;Red&gt;Valhalla&lt;White&gt; are slowly returning,
and with that, the town reclaims its former
prosperous, lively demeanor.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262768</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_250_020_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしたちは
『なりきり士』のお仕事を
始めました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We started our job as Roleplayers in this town.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_250_020_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>子どもの面倒みたりとか、
犬のお散歩、とか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We do things like babysitting
children or walking dogs.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>267108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_250_020_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あんまり『なりきり士』の
力とは関係ないけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Things that have nothing to do with
our Roleplayer powers, of course.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>267108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_250_020_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……うん。
なんとかやってます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Still, we have to do what we can.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
